
Motivation(How it started)
==========================

Act as a unified platform for handling all the real time data feeds a large company might have.
This would mean the follwoing:

main parameters wanted(
      high-throughput, 
			large data block,
			low-latency,
      support partitioned, distributed, real-time processing >> led to partitioning and consumer model
			)

These use cases led to a disign with uique elements, more akin to a database log than a traditional messaging system. Some elements of the design.


Persistence
Efficiency
The Producer
The Consumer
Message Delivery Semantics
Replication
Log Compaction



